## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias inherent in opinion pieces and politically charged discussions. The perspectives gathered may not fully represent the entire spectrum of opinions on CRT, particularly those from marginalized communities who may have different views on the theory's impact and importance. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of the debate around CRT means that new developments may not be captured in this report.